sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (OCTT)
    participant CS as Central System (SUT)

    Note over CP,CS: Test Case: TC_045_1_CSMS
    Note over CP,CS: Get Diagnostics
    Note over CP,CS: Reference: Table 164, Section 3.16.1, pages 141-142/176 (PDF pages 38-39/73)
    Note over CP,CS: Prerequisite: n/a

    CS->>CP: 1. GetDiagnostics.req
    Note left of CS: location: URI for upload<br/>(Optional: retries, retryInterval,<br/>startTime, stopTime)

    CP-->>CS: 2. GetDiagnostics.conf
    Note right of CP: fileName: name of diagnostics file (optional)

    Note over CP: [Charge Point starts uploading diagnostics log]

    CP->>CS: 3. DiagnosticsStatusNotification.req
    Note right of CP: status: "Uploading"

    CS-->>CP: 4. DiagnosticsStatusNotification.conf
    Note left of CS: (empty response)

    Note over CP: [Charge Point finishes uploading diagnostics log]

    CP->>CS: 5. DiagnosticsStatusNotification.req
    Note right of CP: status: "Uploaded"

    CS-->>CP: 6. DiagnosticsStatusNotification.conf
    Note left of CS: (empty response)

    Note over CP,CS: Expected result: CP has uploaded diagnostics log<br/>to the location sent in step 1
